{"type":"text","timestamp":1782714448917,"sessionID":"ses_0edf0e6a8ffeZGh67oT6rCLSny","part":{"id":"prt_f120f9add001p8BDPRpUd3CYZw","messageID":"msg_f120f871b001FG4FrDHylTvsm0","sessionID":"ses_0edf0e6a8ffeZGh67oT6rCLSny","type":"text","text":"The source profile screen is intentionally shallow: static identity, inert edit/cards, back, and logout that flips persisted login state then clears navigation back to onboarding. The target already mirrors most behavior, so I’m verifying whether the remaining whole-project finding is really about missing behavior or about weak structure/evidence around those endpoints and tests.","time":{"start":1782714440413,"end":1782714448915}}}
